channel.title: A Great Game,
channel.description:
Tribal Wars is a browserbased online game. Every player controls a small village, striving for power and glory.
What you can do,
Establish a village, join a tribe, help your friends, fight your enemies!
Pretty much you make a town, get an army and go to war with other players kill their men take their resources and even jack their town and keep it for your own. :lol:
[size=4][url=http://www.tribalwars.net/105976.html]Click Here For The Game[/url][/size]
